Do I have to study Computer Science?
Do I need to come with a team?
Is there a Code of Conduct?

frontmatter.full_description: Some of you lot have never written a line of code, and others of you spend your weekends writing C for fun (you're insane). A coding event that suits everyone sounds impossible, right? Think again. We'll have pizzas, games and a CTF style coding challenge for everyone who wants to get involved. There'll be prizes for the quickest team to finish!
